{"type":"message","id":"54fa0393","parentId":"4c7bc457","timestamp":"2026-04-25T03:02:57.303Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System (untrusted): [2026-04-25 00:15:47 GMT+8] Exec completed (fast-she, code 0) :: Using openai / gpt-image-1 for single Switch model: --model <id> | EXTEND.md default_model.openai | env OPENAI_IMAGE_MODEL /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/generated-im…\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"openclaw-weixin:1777086138644-283d861b\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-04-25 11:02 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nA food specimen dissected and displayed like a museum naturalist discovery. One half preserves the outer surface with its natural texture and color; the other half is cut to the core, revealing the internal structure in sharp detail. The background is pure black velvet. The food floats in the frame like something precious and dangerous. Annotated labels hug the structural edges in handwritten serif typography, never floating. Each annotation has three lines: structure name, composition data, and a plain-language explanation. Main title in warm ivory uppercase at the top-left. Overall aesthetic: Audubon naturalist illustration meets Caravaggio lighting meets the most beautiful scientific photography ever made. 4K precision, specimen lighting, extreme internal detail. Realistic style, not diagram, not cartoon. Every material has true physical texture: rough, smooth, wet, dry, dense, porous."}],"timestamp":1777086177235}}
{"type":"message","id":"a8f5bbd2","parentId":"54fa0393","timestamp":"2026-04-25T03:03:08.040Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这段提示词已经很强了，我帮你整理成一个更适合直接喂给图像模型的版本：\n\n**Prompt**\nA single food specimen, dissected and displayed like a rare museum naturalist discovery. One half preserves the untouched outer surface with its true natural texture, skin, color, and imperfections. The other half is cut cleanly to the core, revealing the internal structure in extreme sharp detail, with realistic layers, fibers, moisture, pores, density, seeds, membranes, or flesh depending on the specimen. The specimen floats against a pure black velvet background, lit like something precious, mysterious, and slightly dangerous.\n\nAnnotated labels are placed tightly along the structural edges of the specimen, never floating far away, in elegant handwritten serif typography. Each annotation contains exactly three lines: the structure name, composition data, and a plain-language explanation. A main title appears at the top-left in warm ivory uppercase.\n\nVisual style: Audubon naturalist illustration fused with Caravaggio dramatic lighting and the finest contemporary scientific photography. Hyper-realistic, 4K precision, specimen lighting, extreme internal detail, dramatic shadow, rich tactile surfaces, true physical material rendering. Every visible material must feel physically real: rough, smooth, wet, dry, dense, porous, fibrous, glossy, matte. Realistic style only, not a diagram, not cartoon, not flat graphic.\n\n**Negative prompt**\ncartoon, illustration diagram, infographic, flat design, CGI look, plastic texture, blurry interior, low detail, floating labels, random text blocks, futuristic UI, white background, extra objects, plate, table, kitchen scene, human hands, oversaturated colors, fake anatomy, symmetrical cutaway, childish style\n\n如果你愿意，我还可以继续帮你做 3 个版本：\n1. **更适合 GPT Image / Midjourney 的短版**\n2. **更适合 Flux / SDXL 的摄影版**\n3. **针对具体食物**，比如柠檬、石榴、牛油果、蘑菇，直接写成可生成的成品 prompt。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_00307533e672fab70169ec2ee3f28c81949ab608b70d891dca\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":23431,"output":436,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23867,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777086177303,"responseId":"resp_00307533e672fab70169ec2ee313708194ac03a8ff80747cb5"}}
