{"type":"message","id":"d4f1b75a","parentId":"3bda491c","timestamp":"2026-04-25T03:05:48.395Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好，我直接给你 3 套可用版。\n\n## 1. GPT Image / Midjourney 短版\n\n**Prompt**\nA food specimen dissected and presented like a museum naturalist discovery. One half shows the intact exterior with natural skin, color, and texture, the other half is cut open to reveal the inner structure in extreme detail. Floating on a pure black velvet background, lit like a precious and dangerous scientific specimen. Edge-hugging handwritten serif annotations, each with three lines: structure name, composition data, plain-language explanation. Warm ivory uppercase title at top-left. Audubon naturalist illustration meets Caravaggio lighting meets ultra-realistic scientific photography. 4K, dramatic specimen lighting, tactile realism, rich textures, wet and dry surfaces, dense and porous structures, realistic not cartoon.\n\n**Negative**\ncartoon, flat graphic, infographic, plastic CGI, blurry details, floating labels, extra props, kitchen scene, plate, hands, white background\n\n---\n\n## 2. Flux / SDXL 摄影版\n\n**Prompt**\nUltra-realistic scientific specimen photography of a single dissected food object, isolated against pure black velvet. One half remains intact with authentic outer texture, blemishes, and color variation; the other half is precisely cut to expose the full internal anatomy with microscopic clarity. Strong chiaroscuro lighting inspired by Caravaggio, combined with the compositional elegance of an Audubon naturalist plate. The object appears suspended in darkness like a rare discovery. Handwritten serif annotation labels sit tightly along the contour edges, integrated into the composition rather than floating, each label containing exactly three lines: structure name, composition data, plain-language explanation. Warm ivory title in uppercase at top-left. Extreme texture fidelity, moist flesh, fibrous membranes, porous layers, glossy seeds, rough rind, subtle imperfections, high contrast, 4K, masterpiece realism, not diagrammatic.\n\n**Negative**\nillustration, cartoon, vector, flat design, fake text blocks, HUD, sci-fi overlay, plastic surface, synthetic lighting, low detail cross section, cutaway diagram, plate, table, utensils, human presence\n\n---\n\n## 3. 直接可生成的具体食物版本\n\n### A. 柠檬\n**Prompt**\nA single lemon displayed as a dissected museum specimen. One half remains whole, showing its dimpled yellow rind with natural pores and imperfections; the other half is sliced open to reveal translucent pulp vesicles, thick pith, radial membranes, juice sacs, and central core in exquisite scientific detail. The lemon floats against a pure black velvet background under dramatic Caravaggio-style specimen lighting. Elegant handwritten serif annotations hug the lemon’s edges, each with exactly three lines: structure name, composition data, plain-language explanation. Main title in warm ivory uppercase at top-left: LEMON SPECIMEN. Audubon naturalist plate meets luxury scientific photography. Hyper-real, 4K, wet citrus flesh, rough rind, porous pith, glossy juice, dangerous beauty, realistic not cartoon.\n\n---\n\n### B. 石榴\n**Prompt**\nA single pomegranate dissected and presented like a rare natural history specimen. One half preserves the leathery red outer skin with cracks, mottling, and crown detail; the other half is cut open to expose densely packed ruby arils, pale membranes, internal chambers, and fibrous core with extreme realism. Suspended over a pure black velvet background, illuminated with dramatic Caravaggio chiaroscuro lighting. Handwritten serif annotations cling to the specimen edges, never floating, each with exactly three lines: structure name, composition data, plain-language explanation. Warm ivory uppercase title at top-left: POMEGRANATE SPECIMEN. Audubon illustration sensibility fused with the most beautiful scientific photography. 4K precision, jewel-like translucency, wet seeds, dry membrane, rough skin, realistic not diagram.\n\n---\n\n### C. 牛油果\n**Prompt**\nA single avocado shown as a dissected museum specimen. One half retains the dark pebbled skin with natural irregularities; the other half is cut to reveal buttery green flesh, gradient color shifts, the seed cavity, fibrous traces, and dense moist interior in sharp scientific detail. The avocado floats against pure black velvet, lit with dramatic specimen lighting inspired by Caravaggio. Handwritten serif annotations sit tightly along the structure edges, each with exactly three lines: structure name, composition data, plain-language explanation. Main title in warm ivory uppercase at top-left: AVOCADO SPECIMEN. Audubon naturalist elegance meets ultra-luxury scientific realism. 4K, tactile surfaces, moist dense flesh, rough skin, subtle gloss, realistic not cartoon.\n\n---\n\n### D. 蘑菇\n**Prompt**\nA single wild mushroom displayed like a dissected scientific specimen. One half preserves the outer cap surface and stem texture with natural dryness, pores, and subtle damage; the other half is cut vertically to expose the gills, flesh, cap layers, stem fibers, and internal density in extreme detail. Floating against a pure black velvet background, illuminated with moody Caravaggio-style lighting. Handwritten serif annotations hug the edges of the mushroom structure, each with exactly three lines: structure name, composition data, plain-language explanation. Main title in warm ivory uppercase at top-left: MUSHROOM SPECIMEN. Audubon naturalist composition fused with world-class scientific macro photography. Hyper-realistic, 4K, porous, fibrous, velvety, damp and dry textures, realistic not cartoon.\n\n如果你要，我下一步可以直接继续帮你做两件事之一：\n\n1. **把这套 prompt 改成更适合中文模型的中文版本**\n2. **直接给你 10 个最适合这种风格的食物选题清单**，每个都附成品 prompt","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_00307533e672fab70169ec2f765bfc8194b264358de3872105\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":23933,"output":1203,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25136,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777086323920,"responseId":"resp_00307533e672fab70169ec2f7561888194bba90ad06e846b2b"}}
