{"type":"message","id":"e294baba","parentId":"de9a7d27","timestamp":"2026-04-25T03:48:22.147Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好，那我先不折腾这条原生线路了。\n\n接下来我默认继续用 **baoyu 这套可用生图链路**，而且你之前已经切好了默认模型，所以我会按这个来：\n\n- **技能链路**：`baoyu-imagine`\n- **默认模型**：`openai / gpt-image-2`\n\n你后面只要直接说：\n- “生成一张……”\n- “改成……风格”\n- “再来一版”\n\n我就直接帮你出图，不再拿那条原生线路打扰你。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_00307533e672fab70169ec3983756c8194a6861a5ddd08e500\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":56037,"output":132,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56169,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777088894505,"responseId":"resp_00307533e672fab70169ec398096b08194a57b95d1f3dc78a1"}}
