{"type":"message","id":"b0b7b19c","parentId":"8f77c70d","timestamp":"2026-04-25T03:48:49.436Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"openclaw-weixin:1777088925471-4dbaad4a\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-04-25 11:48 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nHelp me generate a realistic reproduction of a famous classical painting masterpiece. Create an authentic-looking artwork that captures the original's composition, color palette, brushwork technique, aging effects, and period-appropriate materials. The result should look like a genuine historical artifact with natural patina, canvas texture, and period-correct framing."}],"timestamp":1777088929174}}
{"type":"message","id":"25af442e","parentId":"b0b7b19c","timestamp":"2026-04-25T03:49:05.737Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我不能帮你生成“某幅知名经典名画的逼真复刻版”，尤其不能做成像真文物、真原作那样的仿作效果，这会太接近艺术品伪造。\n\n但我可以马上帮你改成**安全且非常接近你想要气质**的版本。你可以直接拿去用 baoyu 生图：\n\n## 安全替代版 Prompt\n\nCreate an original classical oil painting inspired by the visual language of old master European art, but not a copy or close reproduction of any specific famous painting. Use a historically plausible composition, dramatic lighting, period-appropriate color palette, visible brushwork, aged varnish, craquelure, canvas texture, subtle patina, and authentic-looking museum presentation. The work should feel like a newly discovered 17th-century masterpiece with believable materials and antique framing, but it must be entirely original in subject, arrangement, and details.\n\n## 更强调“博物馆藏品感”的版本\n\nCreate an original museum-quality antique oil painting in the spirit of classical European old masters. Use baroque-style composition, chiaroscuro lighting, restrained historical colors, hand-painted texture, aged varnish, fine craquelure, worn canvas grain, natural patina, and an ornate period-correct frame. The image should resemble a believable historical artifact from a museum collection, but it must not copy or closely imitate any specific known artwork.\n\n## 负面提示词\n\nexact copy, replica, reproduction of a specific painting, forged artwork, modern objects, digital art look, flat lighting, plastic texture, cartoon, low detail, clean new canvas, contemporary framing, photorealistic photography\n\n如果你愿意，我现在可以直接继续帮你做两件事里的一个：\n\n1. **把这段改成更适合 baoyu / gpt-image-2 的最终生图版**\n2. **指定成某种古典流派气质**，比如：\n   - 卡拉瓦乔式\n   - 伦勃朗式\n   - 维米尔式\n   - 提香式\n   - 巴洛克宗教画式\n\n你要的话，直接回我一句：  \n**“改成 gpt-image-2 最终版”**  \n或者  \n**“改成卡拉瓦乔式最终版”**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_00307533e672fab70169ec39a5ee288194a2df9bc192714e64\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":56299,"output":493,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56792,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777088929437,"responseId":"resp_00307533e672fab70169ec39a3d69881949571f79de5f9538e"}}
