{"type":"message","id":"7ffbd83a","parentId":"8f88c460","timestamp":"2026-04-25T03:51:49.846Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"可以，我给你改成**卡拉瓦乔气质、但不复刻具体名作**的安全最终版，直接适合拿去生图。\n\n## Prompt\n\nCreate an original classical oil painting in the spirit of Caravaggio, but not a copy or close reproduction of any specific artwork. Use dramatic chiaroscuro lighting, deep shadow, concentrated illumination, strong emotional realism, and a historically plausible baroque composition. The painting should feel like a newly discovered 17th-century masterpiece, with authentic oil brushwork, restrained earth-tone palette, subtle reds and golds, aged varnish, fine craquelure, visible canvas texture, natural patina, and an ornate period-correct frame. The result should look like a believable museum artifact with old-master materials and atmosphere, but the subject, composition, and details must be entirely original.\n\n## Negative Prompt\n\nspecific famous painting, exact copy, replica, forged artwork, modern objects, modern clothing, photography, CGI, cartoon, flat lighting, clean new canvas, contemporary frame, neon colors, digital illustration, low detail\n\n## 中文加强版补充词\n\n卡拉瓦乔式明暗对照，巴洛克宗教绘画气质，深色背景，聚光式照明，强烈戏剧张力，真实油画笔触，旧油画裂纹，陈旧清漆层，博物馆藏品质感，历史感，厚重，肃穆，古典，原创新构图\n\n如果你愿意，我下一步可以直接继续给你：\n1. **更适合 gpt-image-2 的短版**\n2. **直接指定一个题材**，比如“持果实的少年”“烛光中的静物”“宗教场景感的人像”  \n这样会更容易出图。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_00307533e672fab70169ec3a4e769081949f150d7260201e60\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":56864,"output":382,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57246,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777089099186,"responseId":"resp_00307533e672fab70169ec3a4ce0b48194abc696c00535dbdb"}}
